msgid "SLA material"
msgstr "SLA material"

#: src/libslic3r/Preset.cpp:2080 src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigSnapshotDialog.cpp:83
msgid "printer"
msgstr "tiskalnik"

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:561
msgid "All objects are outside of the print volume."
msgstr "Vsi objekti so zunaj prostornine tiskanja."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:564
msgid "The supplied settings will cause an empty print."
msgstr "Priložene nastavitve bodo povzročile prazen tisk."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:602
msgid ""
"Auto speed requires every filament to have a Max volumetric flow set. Check "
"your Filament Settings."
msgstr ""
"Samodejna hitrost zahteva, da ima vsak filament nastavljen največji "
"volumetrični pretok. Preverite nastavitve filamenta."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:614
msgid "Ironing speed cannot be 0. Set an explicit speed or disable ironing."
msgstr ""
"Hitrost likanja ne sme biti 0. Nastavite izrecno hitrost ali onemogočite "
"likanje."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:621
msgid ""
"Avoid crossing perimeters option and avoid crossing curled overhangs option "
"cannot be both enabled together."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti izogibanja prečkanju obodov in izogibanja prečkanju zvitih previsov "
"ni mogoče omogočiti hkrati."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:631
msgid ""
"Only a single object may be printed at a time in Spiral Vase mode. Either "
"remove all but the last object, or enable sequential mode by "
"\"complete_objects\"."
msgstr ""
"V načinu spiralne vaze je hkrati mogoče natisniti samo en objekt. Odstranite "
"vse objekte razen zadnjega ali omogočite zaporedni način z "
"\"complete_objects\"."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:635
msgid ""
"The Spiral Vase option can only be used when printing single material "
"objects."
msgstr ""
"Možnost spiralne vaze je mogoče uporabiti samo pri tiskanju objektov iz "
"enega materiala."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:639
msgid ""
"Machine limits cannot be emitted to G-Code when Klipper firmware flavor is "
"used. Change the value of machine_limits_usage."
msgstr ""
"Omejitev stroja ni mogoče poslati v kodo G, ko se uporablja Klipper privdih "
"g-kode. Spremenite vrednost machine_limits_usage."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:676
#, boost-format
msgid ""
"While the object %1% itself fits the build volume, it exceeds the maximum "
"build volume height because of material shrinkage compensation."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav se objekt %1% sam prilega prostornini tiskanja, presega največjo "
"višino prostornine tiskanja zaradi kompenzacije krčenja materiala."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:682
#, boost-format
msgid "The object %1% exceeds the maximum build volume height."
msgstr "Objekt %1% presega največjo višino prostornine tiskanja."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:690
#, boost-format
msgid ""
"While the object %1% itself fits the build volume, its last layer exceeds "
"the maximum build volume height."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav se objekt %1% sam prilega prostornini tiskanja, njegova zadnja plast "
"presega največjo višino prostornine tiskanja."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:694
msgid ""
"You might want to reduce the size of your model or change current print "
"settings and retry."
msgstr ""
"Morda boste želeli zmanjšati velikost modela ali spremeniti trenutne "
"nastavitve tiskanja in poskusiti znova."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:712
msgid "Variable layer height is not supported with Organic supports."
msgstr "Spremenljiva višina plasti in podprta pri organskih podporah."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:735
msgid ""
"The wipe tower is only supported if all extruders use filaments of the same "
"diameter."
msgstr ""
"Čistilni stolp je podprt samo, če vsi ekstruderji uporabljajo filamente "
"enakega premera."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:744
msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower is currently only supported for the oozeBot Rapid, Marlin, "
"Klipper, RepRap/Sprinter, RepRapFirmware and Repetier G-code flavors."
msgstr ""
"Čistilni stolp je trenutno podprt samo za različice G-kode oozeBot Rapid, "
"Marlin, Klipper, RepRap/Sprinter, RepRapFirmware in Repetier."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:747
msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower is currently only supported with the relative extruder "
"addressing (use_relative_e_distances=1)."
msgstr ""
"Stolp za brisanje je trenutno podprt le z relativnim naslavljanjem "
"iztiskavanja (use_relative_e_distances=1)."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:750
msgid ""
"Ooze prevention is only supported with the wipe tower when "
"'single_extruder_multi_material' is off."
msgstr ""
"Preprečevanje izcejanja je s čistilnim stolpom podprto samo, kadar je "
"'single_extruder_multi_material' izklopljen."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:752
msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower currently does not support volumetric E (use_volumetric_e=0)."
msgstr ""
"Stolp za brisanje trenutno ne podpira prostorninskega E (use_volumetric_e=0)."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:754
msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower is currently not supported for multimaterial sequential "
"prints."
msgstr ""
"Stolp za brisanje trenutno ni podprt za več materialne zaporedne tiske."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:768
msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower is only supported for multiple objects if they have equal "
"layer heights"
msgstr ""
"Stolp za brisanje je za več predmetov podprt le, če imajo enake višine plasti"

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:771
msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower is only supported for multiple objects if they are printed "
"over an equal number of raft layers"
msgstr ""
"Stolp za brisanje je za več predmetov podprt le, če so natisnjeni na enakem "
"številu slojev splava"

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:775
msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower is only supported for multiple objects if they are printed "
"with the same support_material_contact_distance"
msgstr ""
"Čistilni stolp je za več objektov podprt samo, če se tiskajo z enakim "
"support_material_contact_distance"

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:777
msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower is only supported for multiple objects if they are sliced "
"equally."
msgstr ""
"Stolp za brisanje je za več predmetov podprt le, če so razrezani enako."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:810
msgid ""
"The Wipe tower is only supported if all objects have the same variable layer "
"height"
msgstr ""
"Stolp brisanja je podprt le, če imajo vsi predmeti enako spremenljivo višino "
"plasti"

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:835
msgid ""
"One or more object were assigned an extruder that the printer does not have."
msgstr ""
"Enemu ali več objektom je bil dodeljen ekstruder, ki ga tiskalnik nima."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:853
#, boost-format
msgid "%1%=%2% mm is too low to be printable at a layer height %3% mm"
msgstr ""
"%1%=%2% mm je prenizko, da bi bilo mogoče tiskati pri višini plasti %3% mm"

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:860
#, boost-format
msgid "Excessive %1%=%2% mm to be printable with a nozzle diameter %3% mm"
msgstr "Prekomerno %1%=%2% mm za tiskanje s premerom šobe %3% mm"

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:891 src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:635
msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower currently supports the non-soluble supports only if they are "
"printed with the current extruder without triggering a tool change. (both "
"support_material_extruder and support_material_interface_extruder need to be "
"set to 0)."
msgstr ""
"Čistilni stolp trenutno podpira netopne podpore samo, če se tiskajo s "
"trenutnim ekstruderjem brez sprožitve menjave orodja. (tako "
"support_material_extruder kot support_material_interface_extruder morata "
"biti nastavljena na 0)."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:901
msgid ""
"Organic support tree tip diameter must not be smaller than support material "
"extrusion width."
msgstr ""
"Premer konice drevesa organske podpore ne sme biti manjši od širine "
"ekstruzije podpornega materiala."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:904
msgid ""
"Organic support branch diameter must not be smaller than 2x support material "
"extrusion width."
msgstr ""
"Premer veje organske podpore ne sme biti manjši od 2-kratne širine "
"ekstruzije podpornega materiala."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:907
msgid ""
"Organic support branch diameter must not be smaller than support tree tip "
"diameter."
msgstr ""
"Premer veje organske podpore ne sme biti manjši od premera konice podpornega "
"drevesa."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:948
msgid "First layer height can't be greater than nozzle diameter"
msgstr "Višina začetne plasti ne more biti večja od premera šobe"

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:953
msgid "Layer height can't be greater than nozzle diameter"
msgstr "Višina plasti ne sme biti večja od premera šobe"

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:981
msgid ""
"Relative extruder addressing requires resetting the extruder position at "
"each layer to prevent loss of floating point accuracy. Add \"G92 E0\" to "
"layer_gcode."
msgstr ""
"Relativno naslavljanje ekstruderja zahteva ponastavitev položaja ekstruderja "
"pri vsaki plasti, da se prepreči izguba natančnosti s plavajočo vejico. "
"Dodajte \"G92 E0\" v layer_gcode."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:985
msgid ""
"\"G92 E0\" was found in before_layer_gcode, which is incompatible with "
"absolute extruder addressing."
msgstr ""
"\"G92 E0\" je bil najden v before_layer_gcode, kar je nezdružljivo z "
"absolutnim naslavljanjem ekstruderja."

#: src/libslic3r/Print.cpp:988
msgid ""
"\"G92 E0\" was found in layer_gcode, which is incompatible with absolute "
"extruder addressing."
msgstr ""
"\"G92 E0\" je bil najden v layer_gcode, kar je nezdružljivo z absolutnim "
"naslavljanjem ekstruderja."

