msgid "Layers and Perimeters"
msgstr "Plasti in obodi"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:459
msgid ""
"This setting controls the height (and thus the total number) of the slices/"
"layers. Thinner layers give better accuracy but take more time to print."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev nadzoruje višino (in s tem skupno število) rezin/plasti. "
"Tanjše plasti zagotavljajo večjo natančnost, vendar je za tiskanje potrebno "
"več časa."

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:466 src/slic3r/GUI/Sidebar.cpp:1709
msgid "Color mixing base layers"
msgstr "Osnovne plasti mešanja barv"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:468
msgid ""
"Number of initial layers that print with a single filament instead of color-"
"mixed dither. The bottom of a print is exposed (glass beds, flipped prints) "
"and the dither pattern produces visible striping until the cycle has had "
"several layers to converge. Locking the base to one filament also keeps bed "
"adhesion uniform on the most critical layers. Set to 0 to disable and start "
"color mixing immediately on layer 1."
msgstr ""
"Število začetnih plasti, ki se natisnejo z enim filamentom namesto z barvno "
"mešanim raztrosom. Spodnji del tiska je izpostavljen (steklene podlage, "
"obrnjeni tiski) in vzorec raztrosa ustvarja vidno progavost, dokler cikel ne "
"potrebuje več plasti za uskladitev. Zaklepanje osnove na en filament ohranja "
"tudi enakomeren oprijem na podlago na najbolj kritičnih plasteh. Nastavite "
"na 0, da onemogočite in takoj začnete mešanje barv na plasti 1."

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:478 src/slic3r/GUI/Sidebar.cpp:1710
msgid "Color mixing base filament"
msgstr "Osnovni filament mešanja barv"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:480
msgid ""
"Which loaded filament to use for the color mixing base layers (see above).\n"
"• Darkest: auto-pick the darkest loaded filament. Hides any dither artifacts "
"and tends to give the cleanest-looking bottom face.\n"
"• Lightest: auto-pick the brightest loaded filament. Useful when the bottom "
"of the print should look bright or be barely visible.\n"
"• Volume default: use whatever filament the volume is otherwise assigned to. "
"Pick this if you want explicit control through the volume's extruder setting."
msgstr ""
"Kateri naloženi filament uporabiti za osnovne plasti mešanja barv (glej "
"zgoraj).\n"
"• Najtemnejši: samodejno izberi najtemnejši naloženi filament. Skrije "
"morebitne artefakte raztrosa in običajno daje najčistejši videz spodnje "
"površine.\n"
"• Najsvetlejši: samodejno izberi najsvetlejši naloženi filament. Uporabno, "
"kadar naj bo spodnji del tiska svetel ali komaj viden.\n"
"• Privzeto za prostornino: uporabi filament, ki je sicer dodeljen "
"prostornini. Izberite to, če želite izrecen nadzor prek nastavitve "
"ekstruderja prostornine."

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:488
msgid "Darkest available"
msgstr "Najtemnejši razpoložljivi"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:489
msgid "Lightest available"
msgstr "Najsvetlejši razpoložljivi"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:490
msgid "Volume default"
msgstr "Privzeto za prostornino"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:494 src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigWizard.cpp:2667
#: src/slic3r/GUI/Sidebar.cpp:3468
msgid "Max print height"
msgstr "Največja višina tiska"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:495
msgid ""
"Set this to the maximum height that can be reached by your extruder while "
"printing."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite na največjo višino, ki jo lahko doseže vaš ekstruder med tiskanjem."

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:503
msgid "Hostname, IP or URL"
msgstr "Ime gostitelja, IP ali URL"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:505
msgid ""
"Slic3r can upload G-code files to a printer host. This field should contain "
"the hostname, IP address or URL of the printer host instance. Print host "
"behind HAProxy with basic auth enabled can be accessed by putting the user "
"name and password into the URL in the following format: https://"
"username:password@your-octopi-address/"
msgstr ""
"Slic3r lahko naloži datoteke G-kode na gostitelja tiskalnika. To polje mora "
"vsebovati ime gostitelja, naslov IP ali URL primerka gostitelja tiskalnika. "
"Do gostitelja tiskalnika za HAProxy z omogočeno osnovno overitvijo je mogoče "
"dostopati tako, da v URL vnesete uporabniško ime in geslo v naslednji "
"obliki: https://username:password@your-octopi-address/"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:514
msgid "API Key / Password"
msgstr "API ključ / geslo"

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:515
msgid ""
"Slic3r can upload G-code files to a printer host. This field should contain "
"the API Key or the password required for authentication."
msgstr ""
"Slic3r lahko naloži datoteke G-kode na gostitelja tiskalnika. To polje mora "
"vsebovati ključ API ali geslo, potrebno za overitev."

#: src/libslic3r/PrintConfig.cpp:522 src/slic3r/GUI/GCodeViewer.cpp:4200
