#: src/slic3r/GUI/Gizmos/GLGizmoColorMixing.cpp:359
msgid ""
"Color mixing painted. Blends look best on near-vertical walls. Top surfaces, "
"steep overhangs, and the base layers may show a single filament rather than "
"the blended target. Base layer behavior is configurable in Print Settings -> "
"Layer height."
msgstr ""
"Pobarvano z mešanjem barv. Mešanice so videti najbolje na skoraj navpičnih "
"stenah. Zgornje površine, strmi previsi in osnovne plasti lahko prikažejo en "
"sam filament namesto zmešanega cilja. Vedenje osnovne plasti je nastavljivo "
"v Nastavitve tiska -> Višina plasti."

#: src/slic3r/GUI/Gizmos/GLGizmoColorMixing.cpp:513
msgid ""
"Color blends best on near-vertical walls. Top faces and steep overhangs may "
