#: src/slic3r/GUI/GUI_App.cpp:404
#, boost-format
msgid ""
"Starting with %1% 2.3, configuration directory on Linux has changed "
"(according to XDG Base Directory Specification) to \n"
"%2%.\n"
"\n"
"This directory did not exist yet (maybe you run the new version for the "
"first time).\n"
"However, an old %1% configuration directory was detected in \n"
"%3%.\n"
"\n"
"Consider moving the contents of the old directory to the new location in "
"order to access your profiles, etc.\n"
"Note that if you decide to downgrade %1% in future, it will use the old "
"location again.\n"
"\n"
"What do you want to do now?"
msgstr ""
"Od %1% 2.3 se je konfiguracijski imenik v sistemu Linux spremenil (v skladu "
"s specifikacijo XDG Base Directory) na \n"
"%2%.\n"
"\n"
"Ta imenik še ne obstaja (morda novo različico zaganjate prvič).\n"
"Vendar je bil v \n"
"%3% zaznan star konfiguracijski imenik %1%.\n"
"\n"
"Razmislite o premiku vsebine starega imenika na novo mesto, da dostopate do "
"svojih profilov itd.\n"
"Upoštevajte, da bo, če se v prihodnosti odločite za razgradnjo %1%, znova "
"uporabil staro mesto.\n"
"\n"
